nodes.text: Ishi Tib-cracked coconuts were a type of coconut which presumably was grown on the planet Tibrin by the Ishi Tib. They were used as donut filling in Iced donut with shredded Ishi Tib-cracked coconut which was served in Dex's Diner on Coruscant. Ishi Tib-cracked coconut flavoured syrup was also added to Fizzyglug to add flavour.
